    "overall settings": {
        "title": "Moon Base",
        "description": "Start with a small <c=gray>base</c> that supports helium-3 mining, with plans to add more rooms for living and working. Investigate <c=gray>Selenids</c> to determine their purpose and where they are coming from.\r\n\r\nCombat imagined by the initial setup is low-key, such as grabbing a nearby iron rod and swinging to dissuade or disable an enemy. It's also detailed, with ways to keep track of injuries to various body parts. <i>Be mindful of your suit\u2014survival requires oxygen!</i>",
